high_descs: pick up the mug that is on the table.
take the coffee cup to the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave.
Turn on the microwave on the sidetable to heat up the liquid inside the cup.
Take the mug out of the microwave and put it back on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Taking your Mug to the microwave to heat up the liquid.

high_descs: Turn your back. Move closer to the sidetable.
Take the mug on the table.
Turn your back. Move forward until the microwave is on your left. Turn to the left and move to the microwave.
Open the microwave door. Place the mug in the microwave. Close the door. Turn on the microwave for a few seconds. After it turns off, open the microwave door and remove the mug. Close the door.
Turn around to your back, move and when you are parallel to the sidetable, turn to the right. Approach the sidetable.
Place the mug on the left, before the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Take a mug to heat in the microwave and return it to the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn around to walk to the sidetable.
Pick up the mug from the table.
Turn right to reach the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave and take it out.
Turn left to walk to the sidetable.
Put the mug on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the hot mug on the SideTable.
